crazy english ( simplified chinese : &lt;unk&gt; ; traditional chinese : &lt;unk&gt; ; pinyin : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2005 chinese film directed by wang &lt;unk&gt; . it was screened in the un certain regard section at the 2005 cannes film festival . the film was selected as the chinese entry for the best foreign language film at the 89th academy awards but it was not nominated .